race.description: Ladbrokes Big Bets Copy Now Handicap (C1)
race.comment: SOUTHERN AURORAS (5) has been busting to win and rates well again. Has an awkward barrier but the top hoop rides for the first time and that can make the difference. BELLA CHINKARA (6) didn't manage the wide gate here last time but brought improving form to that. Has a tricky gate again but peaks today and she will be in the finish with average luck. TRIBAL COUNCIL (2) deserved his Maiden win here and has scope for more improvement. Maps well with a small claim and won't have to be much better to feature. GEEGEES DOWNPOUR (3) didn't manage the wide gate last time but the form prior would see him well in the mix.
